Package: auxiora
Version: 2.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs (>= 22.0.0)
Maintainer: Auxiora Team <team@auxiora.dev>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://auxiora.dev
Description: Self-hosted AI assistant with encrypted vault, multi-provider support, and plugin ecosystem
 Auxiora is a security-first personal AI assistant that runs entirely on
 your own infrastructure. It features an encrypted credential vault,
 multi-provider LLM support, a plugin ecosystem, and workflow automation.
